        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e2e93bffed8e4f056824b8b5"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_affe90522d411d311c01ed09",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "创建一个你的角色需要跳过去的障碍物精灵。",
        "text_hash": "e22b6a29d6672838349149914134ba884c7501cdaa2da2d2c7a76a13ca999845",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e2e93bffed8e4f056824b8b5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a9a057a3115a7d6e1c606799",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!TASK]\n选择任意精灵作为障碍物。本示例使用 Bear-walking，它有几个用于行走动画的造型，但你的障碍物可以按你喜欢的样子显示。",
        "text_hash": "fb741f6527671bd295cc7d696acf98155d09e62071be43e578363067dba9d89e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e2e93bffed8e4f056824b8b5"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_17a48d780373732cc981dd44",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!TASK]\n选择障碍物，然后点击 **代码** 选项卡。添加这些积木来设置它的位置、方向和大小。\nBear-walking 精灵。{:width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\" style=\"object-fit: contain;\"}\nblocks3\n+when green flag clicked\n+set rotation style [left-right v]\n+set size to (25) %\n+go to x: (280) y: (-85)\n+point in direction (-90)\n示例位置会把障碍物放在舞台右边缘之外一点。如果你的障碍物没有贴在地面上，请更改 y 位置。",
        "text_hash": "b4a2b90d44d2d4e92dcdcfe54846f975d09739fd948d06cf311442dd9aef0ba6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e2e93bffed8e4f056824b8b5"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    }
  ],
